==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
A quote from the [[wikipedia:Analects_of_Confucius|Analects of Confucius]].

Literally: If a person lacks consideration for what is long off, he will indeed have worries before too long.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén wú yuǎnlǜ, bì yǒu jìn yōu

===Proverb===
'''[[人]][[无]][[远虑]]，[[必]][[有]][[近]][[忧]]'''

# One should plan for the future, or else get run over by it.

===Alternate forms===
[[人無遠慮，必有近憂]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

